SimCOVID-19

Simulation of the SARS-CoV-2 pandemic virus outbreak which cause the corona virus disease 2019 (COVID-19) by using a modified S. E. I. R. D. model. This repository is currently in a preview state! It should be used with caution! Currently only German data has been processed, other countries will follow. Further questions can answered by soeren.thiering@hs-anhalt.de

Data

Thanks for sharing the data by Johns Hopkins CSSE (https://systems.jhu.edu/research/public-health/ncov/).
